# Governança de agentes (cada prompt)

Contrato completo e checklists: [`specs/agent-ia-governance.md`](../../specs/agent-ia-governance.md). Orquestração das fases: [`specs/agent-session-workflow.md`](../../specs/agent-session-workflow.md).

**Abertura:** classificar escopo; se ESLint / npm do pacote / CI relacionada → consultar [`reference/Clippings/`](../../reference/Clippings/) e [`specs/agent-reference-clippings.md`](../../specs/agent-reference-clippings.md); se Docker / Compose / `.docker/` / `ops-eslint` → [`specs/agent-docker-compose.md`](../../specs/agent-docker-compose.md) e skill `docker-compose-workflow`; se expandir escopo do produto, reler [`docs/limitations-and-scope.md`](../../docs/limitations-and-scope.md).

**Fechamento:** manter [`docs/repository-tree.md`](../../docs/repository-tree.md) alinhado à árvore real; cumprir [`specs/agent-documentation-workflow.md`](../../specs/agent-documentation-workflow.md); na resposta, listar docs alterados ou declarar que não houve necessidade (caminhos relativos à raiz ao listar ficheiros); se houver mudanças locais, [`specs/agent-git-workflow.md`](../../specs/agent-git-workflow.md).

**Skills:** `reference-clippings-workflow`, `eslint-plugin-workflow`, `github-markdown-docs`, `git-agent-workflow`, `reference-agents-portfolio`, `docker-compose-workflow` (em [`.cursor/skills/`](../../.cursor/skills/)); se `reference/agents-ref/` for relevante, leia [`specs/agent-reference-agents.md`](../../specs/agent-reference-agents.md).
